      .content
        h1 Living at Resa
        .wrapper
          p Here, living centers around the Swedish concept of lagom: creating a life that is “just right”. We find pleasure in simple things: a glass of wine with friends, reading by the fire, or lounging on the terrace watching the sunset. Skanska’s philosophy of innovative design centers on the use of inspired, sustainable, and community-minded methods to create dignified and inviting environments where tenants can reside, relax, and rejoice. Our delight in practical simplicity is apparent in our design and spaces, which highlights and appreciates the intersection between beauty and functionality. Interior spaces are simple and uncluttered; they are warm, cozy and welcoming. Välkommen to RESA. 
    
